  "text": "The code attempts to implement the Bellman-Ford algorithm to find minimum path weights from a source node. However, it incorrectly initializes nodes from edge endpoints and wrongly updates edge weights instead of distances to nodes. This causes the paths to not relax properly, resulting in all node distances except the source remaining infinite, hence failing the tests.",
